	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Hail the Engi to see what's wrong.</text>
		<event>
			<text>An Engi wearing a purple party hat appears onscreen. In the backgrounds are colorful rapidly flashing lights and several Slugs dancing. "Commence greetings. Inquiry: knowledge of how to 'party hard'. Request: mind-altering substances for gratification, recommended by Slug visitors."</text>
