				<text>(Ion Weapon) Zap the Engi, it's close enough.</text>
				<event>	
					<text>The Engi flails like a puppet for a few minutes. Once it regains control over itself, its screen begins to rapidly flash colors, and it speaks very slowly. "Graaaaatituuuuuude. Thiiiiiis is: dooooope. Aaaaacceeeeept cooompeeeensaaaaaatiooon."</text>
