				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="BLUELIST_PHEROMONES">
				<text>(Mantis Pheromones) Disperse the pheromones over their ship.</text>
				<event>	
					<text>A steady distribution of the pheromones certainly has... an effect on the crew. You may have given them too much, because now the Slugs are trying to climb the walls and the Engi are hugging the drones. While they're distracted you scrap some of the exterior regions of their ship.</text>
