				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_ORCHID">
				<text>(Orchid Crew) Have your Orchid work some magic on them.</text>
				<event>	
					<text>The Orchids have a unique ability to put others in a... "daze". The effect is visible on the Slugs and Engi who begin to act very strangely. They pay you for your "assistance."</text>
					<autoReward level="MED">scrap_only</autoReward>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CHECKCREW_BUTLER">
				<text>(Butler Drone) Turn it up to eleven.</text>
				<event>	
					<text>It's not exactly what they requested, but they won't complain. The Butler tends to every numerous needs the Slugs and Engi request when they notice it. Soon, it eventually raises the already high volume, and the crew can no longer keep up. Before they all pass out, they graciously pay you for your "assistance."</text>
