<event name="ENCOUNTER_ENGI_ELITE">
	<text>The Engi Defenders are usually non-confrontational, but as their name suggests, their key purpose is to defend the Harmony. One way or another, they have decided your ship poses a threat and move in to neutralize you.</text>
