<event name="DISTRESS_HARMONY_SALVAGE_HELP" unique="true">
	<text>This beacon is littered with parts from Civilians and Pirates, and even a few Engi ships. Only one Elite Engi ship remains, and from the lack of damage you assume it was not involved in the battle.</text>
