										<item type="missiles" min="-5" max="-5"/>
										<item type="drones" min="-3" max="-3"/>
									</item_modify>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Await your reward.</text>
										<event>
											<text>You wait for your reward, but the Engi transfer nothing over. You hail them, to which they respond, "Reward is already present. Gratification and warm feeling for helping others."</text>
											<choice hidden="true">
												<text>What? We will not stand for this!</text>
												<event>
													<text>You aren't about to put up with this garbage. You power up the weapons and prepare to engage the Engi head-on.</text>
													<ship load="SHIP_ENGI_SALVAGE_HELP" hostile="true"/>
													<choice hidden="true">
