<event name="QUEST_HARMONY_ENGINEER_CRIME" unique="true">
	<text>Of all the ships you would have thought to see here, a Rebel Engineer is the last one you would have expected. They're busy inspecting the wreck of an Engi ship, though due to the non-aggression pact between the Rebel and Engi, and the fact that the Engineer's weapons don't match with the damage done to the ship, it's likely they weren't the one to destroy the ship.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Hail them to ask about the wreck.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Engineer sighs, deep in thought. "No, we didn't do this... It's a shame that someone would. I know it's very uncharacteristic of a Rebel to care about something like this, but I didn't join the Rebellion for just a 'glorious human future'. The Rebels fund my projects, and that's all I care about. Someone has been hunting the Engi in this territory, and I want it stopped. Do you think you could inspect the wreck and figure out who did it?"</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Agree to find the killer.</text>
				<event load="QUEST_HARMONY_ENGINEER_CRIME_INSPECT"/>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>We aren't detectives, we can't help.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Expected. This was the second reason I joined the Rebellion..."</text>
					<choice>
						<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
						<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
					</choice>
					<choice>
						<text>Do nothing.</text>
						<event/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Who cares whose responsible? Kill the Rebels!</text>
		<event>
			<text>It doesn't matter if the Engineers didn't kill the Engi, they've no doubt killed plenty others.</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_ENGINEER" hostile="true"/> 
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ignore the Engineer.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Engineer continues to inspect the Engi wreck and ignores your ship.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
